nodes.text: A clone trooper participated in the Battle of Ryloth under command of captain Keeli.

During the battle of Ryloth, this clone trooper and another clone helped set up explosive charges on a hill near a LAAT/i gunship filled with explosives in an attempt to cut off the Separatist advance through a mountain pass. Once the droids discovered the gunship and came to investigate it, the clones, who were hiding in bushes nearby, detonated the explosives and the hills surrounding the pass collapsed and the route became blocked. Later, this trooper was killed serving by Keeli, who died moments later.
